{"tid":420064,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黃子華主演【二月三十】係最好睇既驚慄片","createTime":"2017-10-01T05:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:10:52.000Z","uid":129206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6352b4448f0b50bb6b4b822fc0fc0613ed7c7f4b","tid":420064,"uid":129206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/22/182516_919720265968ee012020f300abc68ea9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F22%2F182516_919720265968ee012020f300abc68ea9.png&h=e5353d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　<br />\n《二月三十》在這系列裡頗特殊，是唯一一部「分段式鬼片」，電影分成兩個獨立故事，由飾演警察「陳查禮」的黃子華串連之，而這次的警察比較像旁觀者，而非以警察查案為主軸。<br />\n　<br />\n睇片：<a href=\"http://vimeo.com/188396297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F188396297&d=124MPmTb5GpcFqLGG2F%2FZDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=322bd92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://vimeo.com/188396297</a>"},{"pid":"2f18c1798f99ffc4995263aa9c948778f4c62d42","tid":420064,"uid":129206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/_x9bPXf77xGc/Sqtm--cnC1I/AAAAAAAAGu8/Nxo9XzpsLLI/s576/0230-04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh6.ggpht.com%2F_x9bPXf77xGc%2FSqtm--cnC1I%2FAAAAAAAAGu8%2FNxo9XzpsLLI%2Fs576%2F0230-04.jpg&h=a1c913e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"893bf062c066f94827436e2f113dc7ef42913c94","tid":420064,"uid":129019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"童愛玲後生係正"}]}